WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to the AccessAbility Community platform.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
We're a safe space for individuals with disabilities to connect and share experiences.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Our platform features Low Energy Mode for users who experience fatigue.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Browse resources organized by specific disability challenges.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Share tips and learn from community members' real experiences.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Built with accessibility at the core - WCAG 2.1 AA compliant.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Join thousands of individuals who understand your journey.
